===Adjective===
'''animate'''
# That which [[live]]s.
# [[Possess]]ing the [[quality]] or [[ability]] of [[motion]].
# [[Dynamic]], [[energetic]].
#:''She is an engaging and '''animate''' speaker.''
# {{cattag|grammar}} having at least one human or animal [[referent]] or [[inflect]]ed to agree with a term that has such a [[referent]]

====Synonyms====
*(''that lives''): [[alive]], [[live]], [[living]]
*(''possessing the quality or ability of motion''):
*(''dynamic''): [[active]], [[dynamic]], [[energetic]]

====Antonyms====
*(''living''): [[inanimate]]
*(''possessing the quality or ability of motion''): [[fixed]], [[immobile]], [[static]], [[stationary]], [[still]]
*(''dynamic''): [[static]]
*(''grammar, inflected for person or animal''): [[inanimate]]

